summary:
Having traveled to many countries,  I am confident to say I have a good understanding of working with diverse cultures and qualify to work in a team,  in a diplomatic way. Growing up within a family hold where I was motivated to be responsible and take full pride in my femininity, I grew up with a belief that I would achieve anything I desire as long as I put my mind to it. This has influenced me to be driven by an entrepreneurial mindset. With inspiration for marketing and advertising, I have recently integrated my International Business Innovation studies with a minor in Marketing and advertising course at Greenwich University, London. I believe determination guides an individual to work hard and achieve what they want.
MY MOTTO:  Always eager to learn more from anyone - regardless of the industry they're working in.
THINGS I VALUE:- Humanity, nature, family
TEAM ROLE (Belbin Team roles):- Analyst, Team player, Coordinator, implementer & Plant 
STRENGTH IN LEADERSHIP SKILLS:- EXECUTING (Achiever, Restorative, Deliberative & Responsibility) STRATEGIC THINKING (Learner)
